CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 3, 1957, pg. B4, reads: "Hail Arnie - Arnie Sowell, champion middle-distance runner and former member of the Ammon track and field team, is presented a loving cup by Judge John Brosky at Homestead High School field, last Friday night. Sowell was the honored guest at a track meet sponsored by Ammon Recreation Center. - Sonney Harris Photo." [mis-attributed?]
TitMainTitle: Runner Arnie Sowell being presented with trophy by John Brosky at Homestead High School field
